overview: Two talent scouts for a New York-based country music TV show called "Square Dance Jubilee" are sent out West to get authentic western singing acts. They find what they're looking for, but also get mixed up in cattle rustling and murder.
tagline: Come on everybody! For the time of your life--get set to enjoy the grandest array of hoe-down entertainment ever assembled in one big happy hit!
title: Square Dance Jubilee
